  "comment": "PRSTAGE LED BAR 424RGBUV is a high-output linear LED fixture featuring 42 multi-chip 4 W LEDs (Red, Green, Blue, UV at 395 nm) with RGBUV mixing, offering over 16 million color variations and long LED lifespan (~50,000 h).\n\nThe fixture delivers smooth 0–100% linear dimming, a wide 60° beam angle, and an adjustable electronic strobe ranging from 1 to 20 flashes per second. Cooling is actively managed (the fan can be disabled via the menu), and built-in thermal protection enhances longevity.\nIts versatile control includes DMX512, sound activation, auto-run programs, and a Master-Slave mode. Available channel modes are 8, and 32 DMX channels. It offers 3-pin XLR DMX In/Out, an LCD display with four navigation buttons, and includes two adjustable barn doors plus a matte plastic diffuser for beam shaping.\n\nPowered via PowerCON (input + through output) from AC 90–240 V (50/60 Hz), it consumes up to 200 W. The robust metal housing measures 610 × 88 × 150 mm and weighs just 3.2 kg",
